sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant Comet as Comet<br/>(TCP/WS)
    participant Logic as Logic<br/>(gRPC)
    participant Redis as Redis

    Note over C,Redis: ═══ Phase 1: 节点发现 ═══

    C->>Logic: GET /goim/nodes/weighted
    Logic-->>C: {WsPort, Heartbeat, Nodes[]}

    Note over C,Redis: ═══ Phase 2: 建连 & 认证 ═══

    C->>Comet: WS /sub → Upgrade
    Comet-->>C: 101 Switching Protocols

    C->>Comet: OpAuth {mid, key, room_id, platform, device_id, accepts, last_seq}
    Comet->>Logic: gRPC Connect(server, cookie, token)
    Logic->>Logic: JSON parse → Session {mid, key, deviceID}

    Logic->>Redis: GET device_session:{uid}:{device_id}
    Redis-->>Logic: old SID / nil
    alt 同设备旧会话存在
        Logic-->>Comet: gRPC Kick(旧连接)
    end

    Logic->>Redis: Pipeline: HSET session / HSET user_sessions / SET device_session / SET key_sid
    Logic->>Logic: async OnUserOnline(mid, lastSeq) 离线同步

    Logic-->>Comet: ConnectReply(mid, key, room_id, accepts, heartbeat)
    Comet-->>C: OpAuthReply

    Note over C,Redis: ═══ Phase 3: 注册 ═══

    Comet->>Comet: Bucket.Put(roomID, ch) — cityhash 分片
    Comet->>Comet: go dispatch() — 写协程

    Note over C,Redis: ═══ Phase 4: 心跳 & 消息循环 ═══

    loop 心跳
        C->>Comet: OpHeartbeat
        Comet-->>C: OpHeartbeatReply
        Note over Comet,Logic: 每 N 次心跳调用一次
        Comet->>Logic: gRPC Heartbeat(mid, key)
        Logic->>Redis: EXPIRE session:{sid}
    end

    opt 消息 ACK
        C->>Comet: OpPushMsgAck
        Comet->>Logic: gRPC Receive(mid, proto)
    end

    Note over C,Redis: ═══ Phase 5: 断连 ═══

    Comet->>Comet: Bucket.Del(ch) → conn.Close() → ch.Close()
    Comet->>Logic: gRPC Disconnect(mid, key)
    Logic->>Redis: Pipeline: DEL session / DEL device_session / DEL key_sid
